metadata.name: Le Chemin Des Illusions
metadata.description:
Black and white room,
Illusions entwined.
Shadows and light,
A captivating find.

Shapes and forms,
In a spectral embrace.
Deceptive echoes,
A monochrome chase.

Truth hides behind,
Veils of disguise.
Illusions dance,
Before our eyes.

Mirror's whispers,
Twisting the view.
Seek the essence,
Within the hues.

In this enigma,
Wisdom resides.
Unravel the mysteries,
Where truth abides.
